Machine-learning model weights
================================================================================

MyAgent does NOT redistribute model weights. Models are downloaded by the end
user at runtime from Hugging Face (and, for Ollama-backed models, via Ollama),
each under its own license. Models referenced by the app include:

  - Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2            (embedder)        — Apache-2.0*
  - onnx-community/Qwen2.5-0.5B-Instruct                 — Apache-2.0*
  - onnx-community/Qwen2.5-Coder-3B-Instruct             — Apache-2.0*
  - onnx-community/Qwen3-4B-ONNX                         — verify on model card
  - hf.co/ggml-org/SmolLM3-3B-GGUF    (via Ollama)       — Apache-2.0*
  - ibm/granite-docling               (Ollama Cloud)     — verify on model card

  * License of the upstream base model; confirm the specific (re-)distribution's
    license on its Hugging Face model card before relying on it commercially.

Because weights are fetched by the user at runtime, they are obtained under the
end user's acceptance of the respective model licenses, not redistributed by
this project.
